294
00:19:15,680 --> 00:19:17,000
I like you a lot.

295
00:19:17,400 --> 00:19:19,920
So, of course, your kiss is a reward.

296
00:19:21,320 --> 00:19:24,840
If I do something right,
you'll reward me, right?

297
00:19:25,520 --> 00:19:27,240
