474
00:29:17,400 --> 00:29:18,320
Let go of me.

475
00:29:19,600 --> 00:29:20,520
I won't.

476
00:29:22,840 --> 00:29:23,840
Let go!

477
00:29:31,680 --> 00:29:34,000
