487
00:30:31,080 --> 00:30:32,000
Xiaoyu.

488
00:30:33,360 --> 00:30:34,920
The person who got the photo

489
00:30:35,240 --> 00:30:38,320
left many comments
in Professor Song's Weibo this morning.

490
00:30:38,920 --> 00:30:40,120
